style=\"color: pink;\">完左遊行入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n入嚟拎大量長輩圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78DSDkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78DSDkx.jpg&h=223461c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16AA7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16AA7e.jpg&h=8266dbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJEa9sf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJEa9sf.jpg&h=7af30e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mn5xDkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmn5xDkB.jpg&h=703812d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTn0yX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTn0yX.jpg&h=53df5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEGdmre.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEGdmre.gif&h=aac3cc53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 七大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b75b19083f33051b06db82f3ccba0fce8458b2c4","tid":1426611,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"大家明唔明白 818 星期日維園集會要full gear上陣點解 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作用就係好似 警察開記者會咁， 啲記者全部full gear上陣。<br />\n<br />\n這就是表態，反映警察會對合法集會或普通平民射催淚彈， 用棍打， 射胡椒球。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家聽日全部要 full gear上陣, 和理非都要。<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴（口罩）, 長遮， 泳鏡， 有頭盔既就帶埋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多本地傳媒同外國傳媒影住架， 效果非同小可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家明唔明白 ？"},{"pid":"010e061898a2171ff4396ba3f74ab095749b9f12","tid":1426611,"uid":222096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274a0d2b6ccc8e2e027b09780723e393a3eebfc5","tid":1426611,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"818<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938695ae9ad75c18ac6bef2517852f0bd059f8b4","tid":1426611,"uid":282449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"同意"}]}